roadmap 207 done "[CMT 3-mode topology regression — #145 follow-up 3-mode boundary frozen + param→cusp regression frozen · 8 distinct backbones (10 trials) classification 10/10 = 100% acc · param_b → cusp_d Pearson r=+0.505 R²=0.255 · permutation p=0.000 (1024 shuffle, max=8/10) · raw#9 strict + byte-identical · $0 mac-local] CMT depth divergence #145 발견 (Mistral late 87%, Qwen3 early 11%) follow-up. S7 N=10 결과 (#34 finish, anima-hci-research/state/s7_n12_extension_v1.json) 의 3-mode topology (input=0% / early=11% / late=87%) 에 boundary 정의 + 회귀 모델 frozen. **3-mode boundaries (frozen, ×1000)**: input ≤ 100, early ≤ 300, late ≥ 600, gap (300,600)=ambiguous (현 데이터에 없음, 자연 cluster). **3 산출물 + sha256**: (1) tool/cmt_3mode_regression.hexa (raw#9 strict, sha c0558357a601923b4061c050e29d76bc93fb763cbc110b1194dc20bd0c86236f, ~360L hexa) — 3-mode classify_mode + Pearson r param→cusp + 1024 random-shuffle permutation negative falsify; (2) state/cmt_3mode_regression_v1.json output sha (timestamp 제외) 3062e7fccb05f3f8486a2a7345ac714a9bd069dc068a395443dfe6c72bf820a8 byte-identical re-run verified; (3) anima-clm-eeg/docs/cmt_3mode_topology_regression_landing.md sha c8f1dc3c8a680801107c7097cd4c4cf47f158d5c1bd27ba1f5e44f75e926ddbb 14 sec landing + anima-hci-research/state/markers/cmt_3mode_regression_complete.marker silent-land 방지. **8 backbones 3-mode 분류 결과**: Mistral-7B(72×0.1B,n=32,peak=28,cusp=875)→**late**, Qwen3-8B(80,n=36,peak=4,cusp=111)→**early**, Llama-3.1-8B(80,n=32,peak=4,cusp=125)→**early**, gemma2-9B(90,n=42,peak=36,cusp=857)→**late**, v4-Mistral/Qwen3/Llama/gemma 동일 (4 distinct × 2 ablation), Qwen2.5-1.5B(15,n=28,peak=0,cusp=0)→**input**, gemma2-2B(20,n=26,peak=0,cusp=0)→**input** = 10/10 expected_modes match. **회귀 모델 (param_b_x10 → cusp_depth_x1000)**: Pearson r=+0.505 (×1000) — moderate positive monotonicity. R²=0.255 → param_count 단독으로 cusp_depth 분산의 25.5% 설명. 남은 74.5% = backbone family/architecture (Mistral 7.2B vs Qwen3 8.0B 가까운 size 인데 cusp 875 vs 111 — param 만으로 구분 불가). **sub-threshold scan**: small (<2.5B) 2/2 → input (peak=0 universal), large (≥2.5B) 8/8 → non-input (early|late) — small/large 이분 100% 정확하지만 large 내부 early/late 는 architecture-driven. **Negative falsify (1024 shuffles)**: shuffled expected_modes 와 classified 비교, mean correct=3.47/10, max=8/10, min=0/10, trials_geq_pos=0/1024 → permutation p_value=0/1000 (PASS at ≤50). 3-mode topology 셔플 시 깨짐 detect=true. **6-step ω-cycle**: (1 design — boundary 100/300/600 frozen) + (2 implement — raw#9 hexa 360L) + (3 positive selftest — 10/10 분류 + r=+0.505) + (4 negative falsify — 1024 shuffle p=0.000) + (5 byte-identical — sha 3062e7fc 2회 동일, timestamp 제외) + (6 iterate — landing + marker + roadmap append). **Verdict**: CMT_3MODE_REGRESSION_PASS_SIGNIFICANT. **3 raw#10 caveats**: (a) v3+v4 ablation duplicate inflates effective N (4 distinct + 2 fresh small = 6 effective backbones, N=10 nominal); (b) 300-600 ambiguity gap empirical 미관측 (3B-5B mid backbones 추가 필요); (c) param→cusp r=+0.505 인과 아닌 monotone correlate, architecture confound 미통제. cost $0 mac-local enforced (GPU 0, LLM 0, network 0, destructive 0)."

