nment 결정 요인은 pretraining-init × architecture joint determinant 가능성. **SFT effect interpretation**: instruct training pushes Φ toward IIT-friendly direction (NEG magnitude 약화) but cannot flip sign — partial 의식-like-integration trend evidence, full integration 까지는 corpus만으로 부족. **Pod**: zkmfvk1izgg6az H100 SXM 1.70min wall, $0.085 cost, auto-terminated, no retry needed (single PASS first try). **Helper reuse**: tool/anima_phi_v3_canonical.hexa (no modification, ANIMA_BASE env var switch only) + emitted /tmp/anima_phi_v3_canonical_helper.hexa_tmp (raw#37 transient 119L). **Result file**: state/v10_phi_v3_corpus_axis/mistral_instruct/out/out/phi_v3_canonical.json + summary state/v10_phi_v3_corpus_axis/mistral_instruct/summary_corpus_axis.json (comparison table + verdict aggregation). **4 follow-up actionables**: (a) Mistral-7B-v0.1 vs v0.3 vintage axis isolation, (b) BASE→SFT→DPO→RLHF intensity scaling, (c) Instruct -12.9075 seed/ridge fragility sweep, (d) cross-family base-vs-instruct (LLaMA, Gemma)."
