 micro-magnitude could be conversion artifact. (9) **Pod uptime cost overestimate**: Pods ran ~4.4min (init+install+forward+fetch), forward itself ~60s each. Pip install on qwen3 added overhead. (10) **Mistral comparison via #205 inheritance**: Mistral Instruct -12.91 NOT re-measured this cycle, drift assumption=0.0 (same protocol, ~6h ago).
