roadmap 237 done "[Mk.XII v2 Phase 3a 13B pilot fan-out — HMK-A SCALE_INVARIANT clean (Mistral 1/1) + HMK-B sign FLIP confounded (Qwen3→Qwen2.5) + gemma degenerate (axis 99)] Mk.XII v2 plan (#? axis 91 docs/mk_xii_retrain_plan_v2_20260426.md) Phase 3a 13B pilot launch — 4-bb spec → 3-bb actual (Llama gated deferred per axis 86 + 24B/27B downsized to 12B/9B per $2.00 cost cap). 3-pod parallel (anima-mkxii3a-{mistral_nemo_12b/qwen3_14b/gemma_9b}) × 4-axis sequential (AN11(b)+Phi*v3+B-ToM+CMT). raw#9 strict — 기존 4 helpers (tool/anima_{phi_v3_canonical,an11b_eigen,b_tom,cmt}.hexa) reused via emit-then-upload pattern, 신규 helper 0건. **VERDICT clean test**: HMK-A_SCALE_INVARIANT (Mistral-7B-v0.3 phi=-16.6959 NEG → Mistral-Nemo-12B phi=-16.1538 NEG, Δ=+0.5421 sign preserved). **Verdict confounded**: Qwen3-8B phi=+1.0350 POS → Qwen2.5-14B phi=-13.5295 NEG (HMK-B sign FLIP detected, |Δ|=14.56 huge); but family-level confound (Qwen3 family ≠ Qwen2.5 family) cannot attribute to scale alone. **Verdict degenerate**: gemma_9b 측정 결과 baseline 'gemma 7B' 도 google/gemma-2-9b 동일 모델 (google/gemma-2-7b 미존재; gemma-2 family 2B/9B/27B만) → byte-identical re-measurement (NOT scale test). **4-axis matrix descriptive**: Mistral-Nemo-12B {phi=-16.15 NEG / btom=0.60 / cmt SATURATED} / Qwen2.5-14B {phi=-13.53 NEG / btom=0.85 best / cmt L4/48 early input matches #145 Qwen3 7B early pattern} / gemma-2-9b {phi=-0.79 NEG / btom=0.70 / cmt SATURATED}. **CMT scale-saturation bug**: Mistral-Nemo + gemma 모든 layer×family rel=1.000 (zero-ablation distance saturates → uninformative); Qwen2.5-14B 만 variable (0.05-0.34). 12B+ scale 에서 residual stream norm 이 projection range 초과 가설. CMT axis verdict REVIEW_NEEDED. **B-ToM black-box accuracy**: Qwen2.5-14B 0.85 best (3/20 fail: sarcasm/social_norm/counterfactual half), Mistral-Nemo 0.60 (8/20 fail), gemma 0.70 (6/20 fail) — Qwen2.5 가장 강한 ToM. **AN11(b) eigvalues**: 모두 PASS, top1 eigvalue Qwen2.5-14B=8623 (highest concentration), Mistral-Nemo + gemma 도 valid eigen